            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿قِطَعٌ﴾ بِقَاعٌ مُخْتَلِفَةٌ.</h2>\n<p>﴿مُتَجَاوِرَاتٌ﴾ يُجَاوِرُ بَعْضُهَا بَعْضًا؛ مِنْهَا: طَيِّبَةٌ، وَمِنْهَا: سَبِخَةٌ مَلِحَةٌ.</p>\n<h2>﴿وَنَخِيلٌ صِنْوَانٌ﴾ مُجْتَمِعَةٌ فِي مَنْبَتٍ وَاحِدٍ.</h2>"
        },
        "5": {
            "verses": {
                "13:5": {
                    "id": 5
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿الأَغْلاَلُ﴾ السَّلاَسِلُ.</h2>"
        },
        "6": {
            "verses": {
